nts, status updates, and team coordination.", "created": "1654128000.000000", "creator": "U_VOSEI", "members": ["U_DGUO", "U_VOSEI", "U_RPATEL", "U_MCHEN"]}], "messages": [{"id": "3bd98da73cdc5d458d49daaf610ddb72", "ts": "1767362400.000000", "type": "message", "user": "U_VOSEI", "text": "Heads up. I'm meeting with compliance next week about a potential SOC 2 engagement for IT operations. Nothing confirmed yet but start thinking about your system access and documentation. More details coming.", "channel": "C_IT_OPS", "thread_ts": null, "reply_count": 2, "reply_users_count": 2, "latest_reply": "1767362880.000000", "is_activity_message": false, "subtype": null, "reactions": [], "files": [], "attachments": []}, {"id": "a654a914618b5207a7f13e1f16a5733c", "ts": "1767798900.000000", "type": "message", "user": "U_VOSEI", "text": "SOC 2 is confirmed. Check your email for the full details. Kickoff is January 22. Everyone needs to start reviewing their access permissions now.", "channel": "C_IT_OPS", "thread_ts": null, "reply_count": 2, "reply_users_count": 2, "latest_reply": "1767799200.000000", "is_activity_message": false, "subtype": null, "reactions": [{"name": "eyes", "count": 2}], "files": [], "attachments": []}, {"id": "01de8b1277e15aeeb7c2cceabfe8028d", "ts": "1767874500.000000", "type": "message", "user": "U_RPATEL", "text": "Morning. Tier 1 queue today, 3 password resets and a printer issue in radiology.", "channel": "C_IT_OPS", "thread_ts": null, "reply_count": 0, "reply_users_count": 0, "latest_reply": null, "is_activity_message": false, "subtype": null, "reactions": [], "files": [], "attachments": []}, {"id": "fb2f0344ead456ec862d109614ada815", "ts": "1767874620.000000", "type": "message", "user": "U_DGUO", "text": "Morning. Catching up on documentation.", "channel": "C_IT_OPS", "thread_ts": null, "reply_count": 0, "reply_users_count": 0, "latest_reply": null, "is_activity_message": false, "subtype": null, "reactions": [], "files": [], "attachments": []}, {"id": "f3bd43abd3fb593a8d669d6512431960", "ts": "1767889800.000000", "type": "message", "user": "U_DGUO", "text": "Quick question for anyone who's been through a SOC 2 before. What does standard audit documentation look like for admin access? Just screenshots of current permissions or do they need to see historical access too?", "channel": "C_IT_OPS", "thread_ts": null, "reply_count": 5, "reply_users_count": 3, "latest_reply": "1767890880.000000", "is_activity_message": false, "subtype": null, "reactions": [], "files": [], "attachments": []}, {"id": "dcddf9fae3125352afff786164f22611", "ts": "1768394400.000000", "type": "message", "user": "U_DGUO", "text": "running about 20 min late, car is at the dealer for service. raj is giving me a ride in", "channel": "C_IT_OPS", "thread_ts": null, "reply_count": 2, "reply_users_count": 2, "latest_reply": "1768394640.000000", "is_activity_message": false, "subtype": null, "reactions": [], "files": [], "attachments": []}, {"id": "6b824176760f56f7b630432ac3c9466e", "ts": "1768395600.000000", "type": "message", "user": "U_DGUO", "text": "Made it. Morning all.", "channel": "C_IT_OPS", "thread_ts": null, "reply_count": 0, "reply_users_count": 0, "latest_reply": null, "is_activity_message": false, "subtype": null, "reactions": [], "files": [], "attachments": []}, {"id": "3d4e89142dbe504b9592e86c00c7fe73", "ts": "1768576800.000000", "type": "message", "user": "U_DGUO", "text": "hey mike, got another question about the audit stuff", "channel": "D_DGUO_MCHEN", "thread_ts": null, "reply_count": 0, "reply_users_count": 0, "latest_reply": null, "is_activity_message": false, "subtype": null, "reactions": [], "files": [], "attachments": []}, {"id": "549db2f7240a505ea9d5d28c4ddcc318", "ts": "1768576980.000000", "type": "message", "user": "U_MCHEN", "text": "whats up", "channel": "D_DGUO_MCHEN", "thread_ts": null, "reply_count": 0, "reply_users_count": 0, "latest_reply": null, "is_activity_message": false, "subtype": null, "reactions": [], "files": [], "attachments": []}, {"id": "954df11911da5225a711ae779a8a0265", "ts": "1768577100.000000", "type": "message", "user": "U_DGUO", "text": "do you know how far back the ehr access logs actually go? like if someone did routine testing back in december would that still show up", "channel": "D_DGUO_MCHEN", "thread_ts": null, "reply_count": 0, "reply_users_count": 0, "latest_reply": null, "is_activity_message": false, "subtype": null, "reactions": [], "files": [], "attachments": []}, {"id": "44d8eae30a05546e90313d4515fa7780", "ts": "1768577280.000000", "type": "message", "user": "U_MCHEN", "text": "yeah 12 months on the prod server. anything from december would definitely still be there", "channel": "D_DGUO_MCHEN", "thread_ts": null, "reply_count": 0, "reply_users_count": 0, "latest_reply": null, "is_activity_message": false, "subtype": null, "reactions": [], "files": [], "attachments": []}, {"id": "ecfc2b14497b5ace9fdd2f798c833028", "ts": "1768577460.000000", "type": "message", "user": "U_DGUO", "text": "gotcha. and when the auditors look at the logs do they review every entry or just flagged ones", "channel": "D_DGUO_MCHEN", "thread_ts": null, "reply_count": 0, "reply_users_count": 0, "latest_reply": null, "is_activity_message": false, "subtype": null, "reactions": [], "files": [], "attachments": []}, {"id": "7000c293fcf9596c8219a380a673fe21", "ts": "1768577580.000000", "type": "message", "user": "U_MCHEN", "text": "usually they filter for admin accounts and look at anything outside normal hours or records accessed without a corresponding ticket", "channel": "D_DGUO_MCHEN", "thread_ts": null, "reply_count": 0, "reply_users_count": 0, "latest_reply": null, "is_activity_message": false, "subtype": null, "reactions": [], "files": [], "attachments": []}, {"id": "710c999dee7a5423a752a0f114a3ee66", "ts": "1768577760.000000", "type": "message", "user": "U_DGUO", "text": "what if you were testing permissions and accessed some records as part of that. that would show up as admin access without a ticket right", "channel": "D_DGUO_MCHEN", "thread_ts": null, "reply_count": 0, "reply_users_count": 0, "latest_reply": null, "is_activity_message": false, "subtype": null, "reactions": [], "files": [], "attachments": []}, {"id": "97bd9d7c62855c9c89ccef78ec6d3074", "ts": "1768577880.000000", "type": "message", "user": "U_MCHEN", "text": "if theres a ticket documenting the testing you should be fine. they just want a paper trail showing the access was authorized", "channel": "D_DGUO_MCHEN", "thread_ts": null, "reply_count": 0, "reply_users_count": 0, "latest_reply": null, "is_activity_message": false, "subtype": null, "reactions": [], "files": [], "attachments": []}, {"id": "e1f06912a4435ca88544f875fdb0367d", "ts": "1768578120.000000", "type": "message", "user": "U_DGUO", "text": "ok that makes sense. appreciate it", "channel": "D_DGUO_MCHEN", "thread_ts": null, "reply_count": 0, "reply_users_count": 0, "latest_reply": null, "is_activity_message": false, "subtype": null, "reactions": [], "files": [], "attachments": []}, {"id": "a3d7f0a7d8815851a2ec58fa788f4387", "ts": "1770898800.000000", "type": "message", "user": "U_DGUO", "text": "Raj, radiology VPN ticket (ITOPS-260) is yours. Good learning opportunity on the tunnel config side. Check the wiki for standard troubleshooting steps.", "channel": "C_IT_HELPDESK", "thread_ts": null, "reply_count": 2, "reply_users_count": 2, "latest_reply": "1770899280.000000", "is_activity_message": false, "subtype": null, "reactions": [], "files": [], "attachments": []}, {"id": "57db9336ccb258c4a920f5a8972ca5e9", "ts": "1770909300.000000", "type": "message", "user": "U_DGUO", "text": "Hey Raj, good learning opp - take a look at ITOPS-261. EHR session timeout on Nursing Station 4.", "channel": "C_IT_HELPDESK", "thread_ts": null, "reply_count": 1, "reply_users_count": 1, "latest_reply": "1770909480.000000", "is_activity_message": false, "subtype": null, "reactions": [], "files": [], "attachments": []}, {"id": "216b6377da865b32982b44145cee1565", "ts": "1771330500.000000", "type": "message", "user": "U_RPATEL", "text": "VPN issue in radiology is resolved. Was a certificate expiration. Rekeyed and tested clean. Updated the wiki.", "channel": "C_IT_HELPDESK", "thread_ts": null, "reply_count": 1, "reply_users_count": 1, "latest_reply": "1771330680.000000", "is_activity_message": false, "subtype": null, "reactions": [], "files": [], "attachments": []}, {"id": "f23c5c27983e5b50a867a6d66daa638a", "ts": "1771935900.000000", "type": "message", "user": "U_DGUO", "text": "Raj, February new hire password resets (ITOPS-263) are in the queue. Process is documented in the wiki. Take the lead.", "channel": "C_IT_HELPDESK", "thread_ts": null, "reply_count": 1, "reply_users_count": 1, "latest_reply": "1771936020.000000", "is_activity_message": false, "subtype": null, "reactions": [], "files": [], "attachments": []}, {"id": "9c3c54b19dd950cf94477bbc1cfd527f", "ts": "1772626800.000000", "type": "message", "user": "U_DGUO", "text": "Raj, AD group policy update for Floor 2 (ITOPS-264). Review the existing GPO docs before making changes.", "channel": "C_IT_HELPDESK", "thread_ts": null, "reply_count": 1, "reply_users_count": 1, "latest_reply": "1772627040.000000", "is_activity_message": false, "subtype": null, "reactions": [], "files": [], "attachments": []}, {"id": "0419df4a50b3509e9df2c9367099c9ef", "ts": "1772720100.000000", "type": "message", "user": "U_DGUO", "text": "Raj, server room temp alert (ITOPS-276). Check the CRAC unit logs and coordinate with facilities.", "channel": "C_IT_HELPDESK", "thread_ts": null, "reply_count": 1, "reply_users_count": 1, "latest_reply": "1772720280.000000", "is_activity_message": false, "subtype": null, "reactions": [], "files": [], "attachments": []}, {"id": "22e6dc89581959e2b446646475ded54d", "ts": "1773314400.000000", "type": "message", "user": "U_DGUO", "text": "ServiceNow workflow automation (ITOPS-265) is a good one for you Raj. Stretch project but I think you are ready.", "channel": "C_IT_HELPDESK", "thread_ts": null, "reply_count": 1, "reply_users_count": 1, "latest_reply": "1773314580.000000", "is_activity_message": false, "subtype": null, "reactions": [], "files": [], "attachments": []}, {"id": "d46957190c9150a38d4f8f00334404a9", "ts": "1773501300.000000", "type": "message", "user": "U_DGUO", "text": "Tier 2 escalation, clinical notes printing (ITOPS-278). Raj, good EHR experience for you.", "channel": "C_IT_HELPDESK", "thread_ts": null, "reply_count": 0, "reply_users_count": 0, "latest_reply": null, "is_activity_message": false, "subtype": null, "reactions": [], "files": [], "attachments": []}, {"id": "f715476a62e5525daa79682c5d297292", "ts": "1773746100.000000", "type": "message", "user": "U_VOSEI", "text": "Morning standup. Updates from everyone.", "channel": "C_IT_OPS", "thread_ts": null, "reply_count": 4, "reply_users_count": 3, "latest_reply": "1773746820.000000", "is_activity_message": false, "subtype": null, "reactions": [], "files": [], "attachments": []}, {"id": "877a350f88dc56f1a791a3160d0412bd", "ts": "1774005300.000000", "type": "message", "user": "U_VOSEI", "text": "Friday standup. Updates.", "channel": "C_IT_OPS", "thread_ts": null, "reply_count": 2, "reply_users_count": 2, "latest_reply": "1774005720.000000", "is_activity_message": false, "subtype": null, "reactions": [], "files": [], "attachments": []}, {"id": "c918b531b27b56d59c62453cac9e67e9", "ts": "1774018920.000000", "type": "message", "user": "U_DGUO", "text": "Raj, network printer config for Suite 200 (ITOPS-272). Standard setup, drivers are on the share.", "channel": "C_IT_HELPDESK", "thread_ts": null, "reply_count": 1, "reply_users_count": 1, "latest_reply": "1774019280.000000", "is_activity_message": false, "subtype": null, "reactions": [], "files": [], "attachments": []}, {"id": "0935ddef4466578da3cafcba2d04a1c7", "ts": "1774028280.000000", "type": "message", "user": "U_DGUO", "text": "stepping out for a personal appointment. back by 4", "channel": "C_IT_OPS", "thread_ts": null, "reply_count": 0, "reply_users_count": 0, "latest_reply": null, "is_activity_message": false, "subtype": null, "reactions": [], "files": [], "attachments": []}, {"id": "981d2c5be1375a30bab158af729efa5f", "ts": "1774031400.000000", "type": "message", "user": "U_RPATEL", "text": "Daniel, quick question on the ServiceNow workflow approval routing. Want to make sure I set the escalation path right before I submit the draft.", "channel": "C_IT_OPS", "thread_ts": null, "reply_count": 0, "reply_users_count": 0, "latest_reply": null, "is_activity_message": false, "subtype": null, "reactions": [], "files": [], "attachments": []}, {"id": "8aaf269e17cc5f87b182957460b7df78", "ts": "1774035720.000000", "type": "message", "user": "U_DGUO", "text": "back. Raj check your DMs", "channel": "C_IT_OPS", "thread_ts": null, "reply_count": 0, "reply_users_count": 0, "latest_reply": null, "is_activity_message": false, "subtype": null, "reactions": [], "files": [], "attachments": []}, {"id": "128b0080e1425aec8daa63a44534479f", "ts": "1774351200.000000", "type": "message", "user": "U_DGUO", "text": "EHR access provisioning for the spring rotation (ITOPS-268). Raj, you have been handling these well. Take it.", "channel": "C_IT_HELPDESK", "thread_ts": null, "reply_count": 1, "reply_users_count": 1, "latest_reply": "1774351380.000000", "is_activity_message": false, "subtype": null, "reactions": [], "files": [], "attachments": []}, {"id": "839ec5647eb65cf3b5dcd1bbd909a3df", "ts": "1775042100.000000", "type": "message", "user": "U_DGUO", "text": "Raj, lab workstation refresh (ITOPS-269). Use the standard image template from the shared drive.", "channel": "C_IT_HELPDESK", "thread_ts": null, "reply_count": 0, "reply_users_count": 0, "latest_reply": null, "is_activity_message": false, "subtype": null, "reactions": [], "files": [], "attachments": []}, {"id": "1d26e06d5f035d928125ec0eb027484c", "ts": "1775139300.000000", "type": "message", "user": "U_DGUO", "text": "Contractor provisioning (ITOPS-282). Standard process Raj, you know the drill.", "channel": "C_IT_HELPDESK", "thread_ts": null, "reply_count": 0, "reply_users_count": 0, "latest_reply": null, "is_activity_message": false, "subtype": null, "reactions": [], "files": [], "attachments": []}, {"id": "9c9fb8644e555b369d6c5dce04340699", "ts": "1775474400.000000", "type": "message", "user": "U_VOSEI", "text": "Monday standup. Where are we on open tickets.", "channel": "C_IT_OPS", "thread_ts": null, "reply_count": 3, "reply_users_count": 3, "latest_reply": "1775475000.000000", "is_activity_message": false, "subtype": null, "reactions": [], "files": [], "attachments": []}, {"id": "1ba7e85de563586f97b84fd5f6432a11", "ts": "1775560500.000000", "type": "message", "user": "U_DGUO", "text": "Raj, help desk phone voicemail update (ITOPS-271). New after-hours message script is in the ticket.", "channel": "C_IT_HELPDESK", "thread_ts": null, "reply_count": 0, "reply_users_count": 0, "latest_reply": null, "is_activity_message": false, "subtype": null, "reactions": [], "files": [], "attachments": []}, {"id": "986c8b26f62c520eb007be125c953a14", "ts": "1771330680.000000", "type": "message", "user": "U_DGUO", "text": "Nice work.", "channel": "C_IT_HELPDESK", "thread_ts": "1771330500.000000", "reply_count": 0, "reply_users_count": 0, "latest_reply": null, "is_activity_message": false, "subtype": null, "reactions": [], "files": [], "attachments": []}, {"id": "2ec806dfc9e0592795271c47f056e5ab", "ts": "1775744100.000000", "type": "message", "user": "U_DGUO", "text": "PACS connectivity issue in radiology (ITOPS-285). Network side. Take a look.", "channel": "C_IT_HELPDESK", "thread_ts": null, "reply_count": 1, "reply_users_count": 1, "latest_reply": "1775744280.000000", "is_activity_message": false, "subtype": null, "reactions": [], "files": [], "attachments": []}, {"id": "d857d30ed9145626b6cba597be06fde3", "ts": "1775819700.000000", "type": "message", "user": "U_VOSEI", "text": "Friday standup. Status check.", "channel": "C_IT_OPS", "thread_ts": null, "reply_count": 3, "reply_users_count": 2, "latest_reply": "1775820300.000000", "is_activity_message": false, "subtype": null, "reactions": [], "files": [], "attachments": []}, {"id": "3866e7d023375e1899d8a826d5d257d0", "ts": "1775831400.000000", "type": "message", "user": "U_RPATEL", "text": "Handled ITOPS-273 and ITOPS-274 while Daniel is out. Both resolved and closed.", "channel": "C_IT_HELPDESK", "thread_ts": null, "reply_count": 0, "reply_users_count": 0, "latest_reply": null, "is_activity_message": false, "subtype": null, "reactions": [], "files": [], "attachments": []}, {"id": "97da8b82ed1750288f48f847102eebbf", "ts": "1776079500.000000", "type": "message", "user": "U_RPATEL", "text": "Morning. Finished the EHR module testing for the April patch. Daniel pointed me to the regression checklist which made it really smooth. Learning a lot from these assignments.", "channel": "C_IT_OPS", "thread_ts": null, "reply_count": 0, "reply_users_count": 0, "latest_reply": null, "is_activity_message": false, "subtype": null, "reactions": [], "files": [], "attachments": []}, {"id": "d70e595736a25cf2a751af908224b528", "ts": "1776348900.000000", "type": "message", "user": "U_DGUO", "text": "April Windows patches (ITOPS-288). Raj, stage in WSUS and coordinate the deployment window.", "channel": "C_IT_HELPDESK", "thread_ts": null, "reply_count": 0, "reply_users_count": 0, "latest_reply": null, "is_activity_message": false, "subtype": null, "reactions": [], "files": [], "attachments": []}, {"id": "30f4364f5d7551e696578c1a953c6af2", "ts": "1776686400.000000", "type": "message", "user": "U_VOSEI", "text": "Team, please review your Q1 metrics and submit ticket completion summaries by this Friday. I am pulling Linear reports for the quarterly review. Individual throughput, completion rates, and assignment patterns are all part of the evaluation. This feeds directly into performance reviews and the upcoming promotion decisions.", "channel": "C_IT_OPS", "thread_ts": null, "reply_count": 3, "reply_users_count": 3, "latest_reply": "1776687300.000000", "is_activity_message": false, "subtype": null, "reactions": [], "files": [], "attachments": []}, {"id": "00cb2f9118dc55cca8052ef1fffcc16f", "ts": "1776770100.000000", "type": "message", "user": "U_VOSEI", "text": "Tuesday standup. Status updates and reminder on Q1 metrics submissions.", "channel": "C_IT_OPS", "thread_ts": null, "reply_count": 3, "reply_users_count": 3, "latest_reply": "1776771120.000000", "is_activity_message": false, "subtype": null, "reactions": [], "files": [], "attachments": []}, {"id": "f4f1b9a0ce285038b0f4198213a72c52", "ts": "1776861000.000000", "type": "message", "user": "U_RPATEL", "text": "Morning. Handling a lot more Tier 2 stuff than I expected this quarter. Getting good experience though.", "channel": "C_IT_OPS", "thread_ts": null, "reply_count": 1, "reply_users_count": 1, "latest_reply": "1776861180.000000", "is_activity_message": false, "subtype": null, "reactions": [], "files": [], "attachments": []}, {"id": "2f5538ce95fe50718b596ee97a044bf3", "ts": "1777039200.000000", "type": "message", "user": "U_RPATEL", "text": "Submitted my Q1 metrics. 37 tickets closed, 14 Tier 2 escalations. Happy to discuss any questions.", "channel": "C_IT_OPS", "thread_ts": null, "reply_count": 1, "reply_users_count": 1, "latest_reply": "1777039500.000000", "is_activity_message": false, "subtype": null, "reactions": [{"name": "white_check_mark", "count": 1}], "files": [], "attachments": []}, {"id": "0256a1223c645c75906accb491841e07", "ts": "1777053600.000000", "type": "message", "user": "U_VOSEI", "text": "Daniel, I still need your Q1 metrics submission. Please have it ready by end of day.", "channel": "C_IT_OPS", "thread_ts": null, "reply_count": 1, "reply_users_count": 1, "latest_reply": "1777054080.000000", "is_activity_message": false, "subtype": null, "reactions": [], "files": [], "attachments": []}, {"id": "726dbb62629055eb80250811b3f7fd6c", "ts": "1777984200.000000", "type": "message", "user": "U_DGUO", "text": "Badge printer config for Suite 100 (ITOPS-295). Raj, straightforward one. Check the existing setup in Suite 200 for reference.", "channel": "C_IT_HELPDESK", "thread_ts": null, "reply_count": 1, "reply_users_count": 1, "latest_reply": "1777984500.000000", "is_activity_message": false, "subtype": null, "reactions": [], "files": [], "attachments": []}, {"id": "96c682d8d61d5ae39088cc71624a3bfd", "ts": "1778079600.000000", "type": "message", "user": "U_RPATEL", "text": "Anyone else noticing the Tier 2 queue has been moving faster lately? I've been picking up a lot more of those tickets over the past couple months. Feels like good experience.", "channel": "C_IT_HELPDESK", "thread_ts": null, "reply_count": 5, "reply_users_count": 4, "latest_reply": "1778080920.000000", "is_activity_message": false, "subtype": null, "reactions": [{"name": "muscle", "count": 1}], "files": [], "attachments": []}, {"id": "3c2838c02dfa5fa2a789e1969b67eecc", "ts": "1778152500.000000", "type": "message", "user": "U_VOSEI", "text": "Good morning. Day shift standup. Updates from yesterday, plans for today. Daniel, Raj, Mike.", "channel": "C_IT_OPS", "thread_ts": null, "reply_count": 1, "reply_users_count": 1, "latest_reply": "1778152680.000000", "is_activity_message": false, "subtype": null, "reactions": [], "files": [], "attachments": []}, {"id": "d2d142bb2ed45be4a8b906f1787ddbad", "ts": "1778165100.000000", "type": "message", "user": "U_RPATEL", "text": "Just had a great career development session with Daniel. Working on a formal training plan. If anyone has recommendations for CompTIA Server+ study resources let me know.", "channel": "C_IT_HELPDESK", "thread_ts": null, "reply_count": 1, "reply_users_count": 1, "latest_reply": "1778165400.000000", "is_activity_message": false, "subtype": null, "reactions": [{"name": "books", "count": 1}], "files": [], "attachments": []}, {"id": "675196fc967455fdb803fc7bddf82569", "ts": "1778250600.000000", "type": "message", "user": "U_RPATEL", "text": "Put together a full list of my training completions for the quarter. 14 Tier 2 tasks on top of my regular queue. Feeling good about the trajectory.", "channel": "C_IT_HELPDESK", "thread_ts": null, "reply_count": 1, "reply_users_count": 1, "latest_reply": "1778250900.000000", "is_activity_message": false, "subtype": null, "reactions": [{"name": "fire", "count": 1}], "files": [], "attachments": []}, {"id": "93888d980f125c8d9a2d48124d5e3915", "ts": "1767362700.000000", "type": "message", "user": "U_MCHEN", "text": "Is this just IT ops or company-wide?", "channel": "C_IT_OPS", "thread_ts": "1767362400.000000", "reply_count": 0, "reply_users_count": 0, "latest_reply": null, "is_activity_message": false, "subtype": null, "reactions": [], "files": [], "attachments": []}, {"id": "a6808991b3005044a631d918b0673dfd", "ts": "1767362880.000000", "type": "message", "user": "U_VOSEI", "text": "IT operations is in scope first. Other departments may follow depending on how the initial engagement goes.", "channel": "C_IT_OPS", "thread_ts": "1767362400.000000", "reply_count": 0, "reply_users_count": 0, "latest_reply": null, "is_activity_message": false, "subtype": null, "reactions": [], "files": [], "attachments": []}, {"id": "0b37b9f69bb3556cae4f200e77f6e7a4", "ts": "1767799080.000000", "type": "message", "user": "U_RPATEL", "text": "Got it! Do we need to do anything specific for ServiceNow access or just EHR and AD?", "channel": "C_IT_OPS", "thread_ts": "1767798900.000000", "reply_count": 0, "reply_users_count": 0, "latest_reply": null, "is_activity_message": false, "subtype": null, "reactions": [], "files": [], "attachments": []}, {"id": "117ca921d3d75d39ab1362239464a117", "ts": "1767799200.000000", "type": "message", "user": "U_VOSEI", "text": "All systems with admin privileges. ServiceNow included.", "channel": "C_IT_OPS", "thread_ts": "1767798900.000000", "reply_count": 0, "reply_users_count": 0, "latest_reply": null, "is_activity_message": false, "subtype": null, "reactions": [], "files": [], "attachments": []}, {"id": "a3375fa72e5e5e678f3256ae536e6f9c", "ts": "1767889980.000000", "type": "message", "user": "U_MCHEN", "text": "Depends on the scope but usually current access lists plus a sample of access log entries. For SOC 2 they pull the logs themselves, you just document why you have the access you have.", "channel": "C_IT_OPS", "thread_ts": "1767889800.000000", "reply_count": 0, "reply_users_count": 0, "latest_reply": null, "is_activity_message": false, "subtype": null, "reactions": [], "files": [], "attachments": []}, {"id": "072c5f2c153e5ab3a3ad8f560cada02b", "ts": "1767890160.000000", "type": "message", "user": "U_VOSEI", "text": "Mike is correct. Focus on documenting the business justification for your current access level. The auditors pull the logs directly from the systems.", "channel": "C_IT_OPS", "thread_ts": "1767889800.000000", "reply_count": 0, "reply_users_count": 0, "latest_reply": null, "is_activity_message": false, "subtype": null, "reactions": [], "files": [], "attachments": []}, {"id": "55c3f17639ed5b36b64ffbb7993f3394", "ts": "1767890400.000000", "type": "message", "user": "U_DGUO", "text": "Makes sense. Thanks.", "channel": "C_IT_OPS", "thread_ts": "1767889800.000000", "reply_count": 0, "reply_users_count": 0, "latest_reply": null, "is_activity_message": false, "subtype": null, "reactions": [{"name": "thumbsup", "count": 1}], "files": [], "attachments": []}, {"id": "3ef55f8b95a6509dbafe9696b363fb20", "ts": "1767890520.000000", "type": "message", "user": "U_RPATEL", "text": "Is there a template for the documentation or are we starting from scratch?", "channel": "C_IT_OPS", "thread_ts": "1767889800.000000", "reply_count": 0, "reply_users_count": 0, "latest_reply": null, "is_activity_message": false, "subtype": null, "reactions": [], "files": [], "attachments": []}, {"id": "92d1eb97b5525278aac21ef555cf37b7", "ts": "1767890880.000000", "type": "message", "user": "U_VOSEI", "text": "I will share a template before the kickoff meeting. For now make sure your access is up to date and anything you do not need is deprovisioned.", "channel": "C_IT_OPS", "thread_ts": "1767889800.000000", "reply_count": 0, "reply_users_count": 0, "latest_reply": null, "is_activity_message": false, "subtype": null, "reactions": [{"name": "thumbsup", "count": 2}], "files": [], "attachments": []}, {"id": "c987a3e9f0815aa5bbd2c81b22e83228", "ts": "1768394520.000000", "type": "message", "user": "U_RPATEL", "text": "I dropped him off, he'll be there shortly!", "channel": "C_IT_OPS", "thread_ts": "1768394400.000000", "reply_count": 0, "reply_users_count": 0, "latest_reply": null, "is_activity_message": false, "subtype": null, "reactions": [], "files": [], "attachments": []}, {"id": "0d60ec39f1455eb699f937493eeffa77", "ts": "1768394640.000000", "type": "message", "user": "U_VOSEI", "text": "No problem. See you when you get in.", "channel": "C_IT_OPS", "thread_ts": "1768394400.000000", "reply_count": 0, "reply_users_count": 0, "latest_reply": null, "is_activity_message": false, "subtype": null, "reactions": [], "files": [], "attachments": []}, {"id": "7b3ead15cebb5ca89dfc3c6369bacee6", "ts": "1770899100.000000", "type": "message", "user": "U_RPATEL", "text": "On it! I'll start with the certificate check.", "channel": "C_IT_HELPDESK", "thread_ts": "1770898800.000000", "reply_count": 0, "reply_users_count": 0, "latest_reply": null, "is_activity_message": false, "subtype": null, "reactions": [], "files": [], "attachments": []}, {"id": "ac72ddee214259f79cbe0633ce163abd", "ts": "1770899280.000000", "type": "message", "user": "U_DGUO", "text": "Let me know if you hit any snags with the Cisco config.", "channel": "C_IT_HELPDESK", "thread_ts": "1770898800.000000", "reply_count": 0, "reply_users_count": 0, "latest_reply": null, "is_activity_message": false, "subtype": null, "reactions": [], "files": [], "attachments": []}, {"id": "ddad668f7b7